WEBVTT

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>GRADUATION CEREMONY</b></Default>

00:00:14.380 --> 00:00:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>KANAGAWA PREFECTURAL
