00:00:16.789 --> 00:00:17.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MARCH 1ST</b></Default>

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobbing]</b></Default>

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:24.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] Yeah!</b></Default>

00:00:24.710 --> 00:00:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY] Mai, is that you?</b></Default>

00:00:32.289 --> 00:00:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi, mister. Do I know you?</b></Default>

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:36.380 line:90% align:center
