00:00:37.039 --> 00:00:40.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY] {\i1}Didn't I dream{\i0}
{\i1}about this before?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:00:42.829 --> 00:00:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF A KNAPSACK KID</b></Default>

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi, mister. Do I know you?</b></Default>

00:00:55.079 --> 00:00:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps softly]</b></Default>

00:00:56.289 --> 00:00:59.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I do look a lot more
grown-up now, don't I?</b></Default>

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[waves crashing]</b></Default>

00:01:03.380 --> 00:01:06.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I guess I do look a lot
more grown-up now, don't I?</b></Default>

00:01:06.959 --> 00:01:08.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mom told me
that I'm not allowed</b></Default>

00:01:08.879 --> 00:01:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to talk to strange old men</b></Default>

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So where is that
mom of yours, anyway?</b></Default>

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, what's the matter?
Are you lost?</b></Default>

00:01:17.829 --> 00:01:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know where I am.</b></Default>

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just don't know where this is.</b></Default>

00:01:22.079 --> 00:01:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't you say
you weren't allowed</b></Default>

00:01:23.879 --> 00:01:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to talk to weird old men
a second ago?</b></Default>

00:01:26.079 --> 00:01:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Fine, then.</b></Default>

00:01:29.790 --> 00:01:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY] This is Shichirigahama.</b></Default>

00:01:33.129 --> 00:01:35.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's much smaller than
the name actually suggests.</b></Default>

00:01:37.670 --> 00:01:40.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a student at
Minegahara High School nearby.</b></Default>

00:01:40.540 --> 00:01:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is Sakuta Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:01:43.079 --> 00:01:45.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now I'm a little better
than a stranger, right?</b></Default>

00:01:47.750 --> 00:01:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

00:01:49.290 --> 00:01:51.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

00:01:57.170 --> 00:01:59.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What's your name, little girl?
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:03.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really don't know who I am?</b></Default>

00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is--</b></Default>

00:02:05.829 --> 00:02:06.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:02:09.629 --> 00:02:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai?</b></Default>

00:02:10.669 --> 00:02:12.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's this? Why so surprised?</b></Default>

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know I didn't
make you wait around</b></Default>

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>long enough to forget about me.</b></Default>

00:02:16.789 --> 00:02:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the real you, all right.</b></Default>

00:02:18.669 --> 00:02:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm asking why you reacted
the way you did.</b></Default>

00:02:20.919 --> 00:02:24.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, there's a little girl
who looks just like you here.</b></Default>

00:02:24.250 --> 00:02:25.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See? She's right there.</b></Default>

00:02:25.710 --> 00:02:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, uh...</b></Default>

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, you saw me standing</b></Default>

00:02:29.379 --> 00:02:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a girl
wearing a knapsack, right?</b></Default>

00:02:31.539 --> 00:02:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I didn't see anyone.
You were alone, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:02:34.669 --> 00:02:36.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean?</b></Default>

00:02:36.289 --> 00:02:37.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was a little girl.</b></Default>

00:02:37.710 --> 00:02:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She looked just like you
as a child actor.</b></Default>

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:41.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was right here.</b></Default>

00:02:41.129 --> 00:02:43.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So do you think
it was really me?</b></Default>

00:02:43.129 --> 00:02:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if it's
some sort of Puberty Syndrome.</b></Default>

00:02:51.039 --> 00:02:52.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? What is it?</b></Default>

00:02:53.500 --> 00:02:55.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm worried. Are you okay?</b></Default>

00:02:55.460 --> 00:02:56.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you hurt?</b></Default>

00:02:56.789 --> 00:02:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[stomps]
-Ouch!</b></Default>

00:02:58.129 --> 00:02:59.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, that hurts!</b></Default>

00:02:59.710 --> 00:03:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you should
keep your hands to yourself.</b></Default>

00:03:02.379 --> 00:03:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or maybe you need
a more thorough examina--</b></Default>

00:03:04.879 --> 00:03:05.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah! Ow, ow!</b></Default>

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:09.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's nothing wrong with me.
Now, can you please chill?</b></Default>

00:03:09.500 --> 00:03:11.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to introduce you
to someone</b></Default>

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:12.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you can be normal.</b></Default>

00:03:12.919 --> 00:03:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:03:24.379 --> 00:03:26.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I want you to meet
Sakuta Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:03:26.789 --> 00:03:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the guy I've been seeing.</b></Default>

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sakuta, This is my--
-I am Mai's mother.</b></Default>

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello. I've been dating
your daughter for a few months.</b></Default>

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nice to meet you.</b></Default>

00:03:36.330 --> 00:03:37.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know about you.</b></Default>

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Mai's scandal first broke</b></Default>

00:03:39.830 --> 00:03:41.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did a full investigation.</b></Default>

00:03:43.419 --> 00:03:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm very sorry
for all the trouble</b></Default>

00:03:45.169 --> 00:03:46.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my daughter caused you
back then.</b></Default>

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I trust
it's been quieter lately.</b></Default>

00:03:49.789 --> 00:03:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No paparazzi
stalking you for photos?</b></Default>

00:03:52.460 --> 00:03:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Yeah</b></Default>

00:03:54.830 --> 00:03:55.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:03:58.789 --> 00:04:00.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to get going soon.</b></Default>

00:04:04.039 --> 00:04:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, dear, the apple might
not fall far from the tree</b></Default>

00:04:06.789 --> 00:04:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when it comes to
your taste in men.</b></Default>

00:04:08.669 --> 00:04:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just make sure
he doesn't cheat on you.</b></Default>

00:04:11.289 --> 00:04:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be fine.</b></Default>

00:04:12.460 --> 00:04:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was very careful
picking him out</b></Default>

00:04:14.539 --> 00:04:16.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I make sure
to discipline him well.</b></Default>

00:04:17.629 --> 00:04:19.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would it be okay
if I called you Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:04:19.790 --> 00:04:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, sure.</b></Default>

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:24.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's self-centered
and causes a lot of trouble.</b></Default>

00:04:24.129 --> 00:04:25.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But please take care of her.</b></Default>

00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I'll do my best.</b></Default>

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:37.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] So today is the last time</b></Default>

00:04:37.750 --> 00:04:40.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be able to go home
with you like this.</b></Default>

00:04:40.420 --> 00:04:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, when did you patch
everything up with your mom?</b></Default>

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:45.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest, we still haven't.</b></Default>

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:48.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though
she came to your graduation?</b></Default>

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never actually
asked her to come.</b></Default>

00:04:51.129 --> 00:04:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then what happened?</b></Default>

00:04:52.879 --> 00:04:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I was filming in Kyoto</b></Default>

00:04:55.129 --> 00:04:58.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one of the child actors
from her agency was with me too.</b></Default>

00:04:58.750 --> 00:05:00.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone else
from your mother's agency?</b></Default>

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:01.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:05:02.629 --> 00:05:04.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And she told me{\i0}
{\i1}the girl was a fan of mine{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:04.959 --> 00:05:06.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}when they stopped by to visit.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That was when she asked me{\i0}
{\i1}what date my graduation was.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:10.579 --> 00:05:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}So that was{\i0}
{\i1}all you said</b></Default>

00:05:12.579 --> 00:05:13.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}then she showed up today?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:16.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}Yep. I thought{\i0}
{\i1}she wouldn't be able to make it{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:16.670 --> 00:05:18.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}because she had work.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:05:18.459 --> 00:05:20.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Mai</b></Default>

00:05:20.629 --> 00:05:22.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you still hate your mother?</b></Default>

00:05:22.540 --> 00:05:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Yeah, I do.</b></Default>

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:26.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The photos I released
when I was in middle school</b></Default>

00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:29.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she snuck in swimsuit shots
without my consent.</b></Default>

00:05:29.790 --> 00:05:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's gonna take a long time
to forgive her for that.</b></Default>

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still</b></Default>

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:38.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are so many things that
have happened in the last year.</b></Default>

00:05:38.790 --> 00:05:40.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I met you, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:05:40.379 --> 00:05:44.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then we had difficulties with
Shoko{\i1}-chan {\i0}and Shoko{\i1}-san {\i0}too.</b></Default>

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But through all of that</b></Default>

00:05:46.629 --> 00:05:48.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was able to find something
precious to me.</b></Default>

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:52.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've had a lot more
important things on my mind.</b></Default>

00:05:52.829 --> 00:05:56.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that hatred of her started to
die down a little bit.</b></Default>

00:05:56.790 --> 00:05:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And besides</b></Default>

00:05:58.879 --> 00:06:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the child that co-starred
with me in Kyoto</b></Default>

00:06:01.829 --> 00:06:03.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was a lot like me.</b></Default>

00:06:04.209 --> 00:06:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I chatted with her mother{\i0}
{\i1}for a bit{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:06.079 --> 00:06:07.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}when I was waiting on standby.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:08.290 --> 00:06:10.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Her father left them{\i0}
{\i1}two years ago</b></Default>

00:06:10.170 --> 00:06:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}so he's not{\i0}
{\i1}in the picture anymore.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:12.790 --> 00:06:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}After that happened</b></Default>

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}the mother started pushing her{\i0}
{\i1}to be more active{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:16.500 --> 00:06:18.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}in the entertainment world.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:18.209 --> 00:06:20.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She didn't like{\i0}
{\i1}the feeling of inferiority{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:20.420 --> 00:06:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}from not having{\i0}
{\i1}a normal family.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:26.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's when she said, "Mai</b></Default>

00:06:26.420 --> 00:06:28.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and can hope to be
in this business."</b></Default>

00:06:29.129 --> 00:06:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really didn't know
what to say.</b></Default>

00:06:31.709 --> 00:06:35.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't bring myself to deny
what her mother is doing.</b></Default>

00:06:35.329 --> 00:06:37.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of them
were still getting along</b></Default>

00:06:37.540 --> 00:06:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they seemed to
work hard together.</b></Default>

00:06:40.709 --> 00:06:43.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] But weren't things
kind of like that for you</b></Default>

00:06:43.459 --> 00:06:45.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-in the past as well?
-Hmm.</b></Default>

00:06:45.290 --> 00:06:47.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't remember much at all.</b></Default>

00:06:47.209 --> 00:06:48.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was really busy back then.</b></Default>

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:51.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I can't believe
she could keep up</b></Default>

00:06:51.209 --> 00:06:54.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with such an intense schedule.
Your mother is amazing too.</b></Default>

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on. Whose side
are you on exactly?</b></Default>

00:06:57.250 --> 00:06:59.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on your side, of course.</b></Default>

00:06:59.129 --> 00:07:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough for now.</b></Default>

00:07:00.329 --> 00:07:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want to talk about this.</b></Default>

00:07:03.170 --> 00:07:04.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Either way</b></Default>

00:07:04.379 --> 00:07:07.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say
I've ever truly understood.</b></Default>

00:07:07.209 --> 00:07:09.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really don't know much
about being a mother</b></Default>

00:07:09.540 --> 00:07:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>trying to do anything to make
her daughter feel special.</b></Default>

00:07:14.170 --> 00:07:15.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One time</b></Default>

00:07:15.170 --> 00:07:16.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my dad said this to me.</b></Default>

00:07:17.540 --> 00:07:20.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"It's okay to not understand
how a parent feels</b></Default>

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until you actually become one."</b></Default>

00:07:24.750 --> 00:07:25.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:07:26.750 --> 00:07:28.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess you're right.</b></Default>

00:07:29.959 --> 00:07:31.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[music playing on laptop]</b></Default>

00:07:31.379 --> 00:07:33.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door opens]
-[SAKUTA] I'm home.</b></Default>

00:07:33.379 --> 00:07:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome back.</b></Default>

00:07:37.420 --> 00:07:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:07:38.709 --> 00:07:39.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. This song.</b></Default>

00:07:39.790 --> 00:07:40.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TOKO KIRISHIMA</b></Default>

00:07:40.709 --> 00:07:42.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Komi told me about it.</b></Default>

00:07:42.379 --> 00:07:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good
if you already heard it.</b></Default>

00:07:44.329 --> 00:07:47.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, Mai was listening to it
the other day.</b></Default>

00:07:47.290 --> 00:07:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it's popular.</b></Default>

00:07:54.750 --> 00:07:55.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps softly]</b></Default>

00:08:00.709 --> 00:08:02.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is this?</b></Default>

00:08:04.290 --> 00:08:05.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew it.</b></Default>

00:08:05.579 --> 00:08:07.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must be Puberty Syndrome.</b></Default>

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:10.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering everything</b></Default>

00:08:10.959 --> 00:08:12.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the cause
of these symptoms</b></Default>

00:08:12.670 --> 00:08:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is rooted with you
or Sakurajima?</b></Default>

00:08:14.579 --> 00:08:16.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I have no idea
how it could be me</b></Default>

00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:19.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'cause I have the cutest
girlfriend in the world.</b></Default>

00:08:19.379 --> 00:08:21.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Afraid that
you might be too happy?</b></Default>

00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:23.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna be even happier
in the future</b></Default>

00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:25.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I don't know
what I'd be afraid of.</b></Default>

00:08:25.290 --> 00:08:27.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a hopeless idiot.</b></Default>

00:08:27.170 --> 00:08:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it comes to the young girl</b></Default>

00:08:28.829 --> 00:08:31.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that bore a striking resemblance
to Sakurajima</b></Default>

00:08:32.330 --> 00:08:34.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were the only one
that saw her, correct?</b></Default>

00:08:34.710 --> 00:08:35.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:08:35.629 --> 00:08:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai wasn't able
to see her at all.</b></Default>

00:08:37.830 --> 00:08:39.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.</b></Default>

00:08:39.250 --> 00:08:41.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's a state
where the two of them</b></Default>

00:08:41.379 --> 00:08:43.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>cannot exist simultaneously</b></Default>

00:08:43.419 --> 00:08:46.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's possible there could be
some causality between all this.</b></Default>

00:08:46.629 --> 00:08:48.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Meaning, the girl disappearing</b></Default>

00:08:48.250 --> 00:08:50.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the moment
Sakurajima came up to you.</b></Default>

00:08:50.500 --> 00:08:51.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I get it.</b></Default>

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:53.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're saying it's like</b></Default>

00:08:53.210 --> 00:08:55.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I couldn't perceive
the two Futabas at once?</b></Default>

00:08:55.789 --> 00:08:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or how you weren't
able to observe</b></Default>

00:08:57.629 --> 00:09:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko{\i1}-chan {\i0}and Shoko{\i1}-san{\i0}
simultaneously.</b></Default>

00:09:00.669 --> 00:09:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:09:01.580 --> 00:09:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As to how all of this relates to
that new scar on your abdomen</b></Default>

00:09:04.879 --> 00:09:07.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I unfortunately have no idea.</b></Default>

00:09:07.210 --> 00:09:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So not even you know.</b></Default>

00:09:09.039 --> 00:09:11.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's been weighing
on your mind that much</b></Default>

00:09:11.419 --> 00:09:12.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why don't you ask Shoko{\i1}-chan{\i0}?</b></Default>

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:15.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, true. I guess
I could try giving that a shot.</b></Default>

00:09:15.960 --> 00:09:17.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think Shoko{\i1}-chan{\i0}
has said before</b></Default>

00:09:17.919 --> 00:09:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she has memories of
experiencing multiple futures.</b></Default>

00:09:20.919 --> 00:09:22.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
I don't want to ask her.</b></Default>

00:09:22.960 --> 00:09:25.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want to do something
to stress her out.</b></Default>

00:09:25.500 --> 00:09:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She deserves better.</b></Default>

00:09:27.210 --> 00:09:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want her to be as happy
as she can be.</b></Default>

00:09:30.580 --> 00:09:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it okay for a taken guy</b></Default>

00:09:32.129 --> 00:09:34.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to say something like that
about a different girl?</b></Default>

00:09:35.710 --> 00:09:36.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's totally fine</b></Default>

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:39.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because Mai and I
are gonna be happy together.</b></Default>

00:09:39.460 --> 00:09:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

00:09:42.210 --> 00:09:43.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi, Mai.</b></Default>

00:09:43.210 --> 00:09:45.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Congratulations on graduating.</b></Default>

00:09:45.250 --> 00:09:47.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:09:47.379 --> 00:09:49.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hang on. Are those pajamas?</b></Default>

00:09:49.919 --> 00:09:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Of course not, you dummy.</b></Default>

00:09:51.830 --> 00:09:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think, "Of course they are</b></Default>

00:09:54.039 --> 00:09:55.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would've been better.</b></Default>

00:09:55.210 --> 00:09:57.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say stuff like that
in front of Kaede.</b></Default>

00:09:57.500 --> 00:09:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be gross, Big Brother.</b></Default>

00:09:59.710 --> 00:10:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I brought reference books</b></Default>

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought Sakuta could use
to study for the exams.</b></Default>

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:06.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I also brought this.</b></Default>

00:10:06.750 --> 00:10:08.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

00:10:08.500 --> 00:10:09.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You're lying!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:10.419 --> 00:10:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}How could they?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:12.419 --> 00:10:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Please, you don't need{\i0}
{\i1}to worry about me.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:15.210 --> 00:10:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}The two of you have already{\i0}
{\i1}given me so many things.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:18.879 --> 00:10:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I've been happy{\i0}
{\i1}and had so much fun.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:21.669 --> 00:10:23.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I felt lonely sometimes</b></Default>

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and really warm{\i0}
{\i1}a lot of the time.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:26.669 --> 00:10:29.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And you gave me this straw hat!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:10:30.460 --> 00:10:32.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai is so amazing.</b></Default>

00:10:32.669 --> 00:10:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Sakuta</b></Default>

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what do you think?</b></Default>

00:10:40.629 --> 00:10:43.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can definitely say for sure
that the current version of you</b></Default>

00:10:43.789 --> 00:10:45.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is much cuter
than the younger one.</b></Default>

00:10:45.879 --> 00:10:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I already know that.</b></Default>

00:10:47.539 --> 00:10:49.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] She looks similar.</b></Default>

00:10:49.129 --> 00:10:50.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Identical, really.</b></Default>

00:10:50.500 --> 00:10:54.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's all the more reason
I feel like something is off.</b></Default>

00:10:54.250 --> 00:10:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean?</b></Default>

00:10:55.539 --> 00:10:58.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is way too perfect</b></Default>

00:10:58.960 --> 00:11:00.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
it didn't feel like you.</b></Default>

00:11:00.919 --> 00:11:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It felt like a version of you
from television.</b></Default>

00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:07.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Well</b></Default>

00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:09.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Huh?
Is that how it ends?</b></Default>

00:11:09.500 --> 00:11:10.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:11:10.419 --> 00:11:11.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:11:11.330 --> 00:11:14.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only had the first volume
sitting around at home.</b></Default>

00:11:14.210 --> 00:11:16.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think Nodoka
might have all of them.</b></Default>

00:11:16.330 --> 00:11:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>KOKONOE (1)</b></Default>

00:11:17.330 --> 00:11:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll ask her about it
next time I see her.</b></Default>

00:11:19.830 --> 00:11:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's an idol
who's your biggest fan.</b></Default>

00:11:22.039 --> 00:11:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm impressed.</b></Default>

00:11:23.169 --> 00:11:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of them
seem to get along pretty well.</b></Default>

00:11:25.580 --> 00:11:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She helped Kaede
with her studies</b></Default>

00:11:27.330 --> 00:11:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until she had
school figured out.</b></Default>

00:11:29.789 --> 00:11:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, let me help out
with something.</b></Default>

00:11:32.129 --> 00:11:33.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Sure.</b></Default>

00:11:33.129 --> 00:11:35.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think you can
cut the onions for me, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:40.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede humming]</b></Default>

00:11:42.750 --> 00:11:44.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not too bad.</b></Default>

00:11:44.129 --> 00:11:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How good does it have to be</b></Default>

00:11:45.580 --> 00:11:47.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before I can get
a compliment from you?</b></Default>

00:11:47.629 --> 00:11:48.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Perfect score.</b></Default>

00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:51.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just need to get better
at memorizing.</b></Default>

00:11:51.169 --> 00:11:52.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

00:11:52.289 --> 00:11:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. That's right.</b></Default>

00:11:56.669 --> 00:11:58.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to give you this.</b></Default>

00:11:58.080 --> 00:11:59.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:11:59.129 --> 00:12:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's call it a lucky charm.</b></Default>

00:12:01.919 --> 00:12:02.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:03.129 --> 00:12:04.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MARRIAGE REGISTRATION</b></Default>

00:12:04.330 --> 00:12:07.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I was a guest on a show
to promote my new movie.</b></Default>

00:12:07.210 --> 00:12:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was a segment showcasing
local marriage registrations.</b></Default>

00:12:10.669 --> 00:12:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The staff gave me
the one they were using</b></Default>

00:12:12.789 --> 00:12:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the show
as a bit of a joke.</b></Default>

00:12:14.669 --> 00:12:16.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They looked me
straight in the eye</b></Default>

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and said I should use this
when I marry that guy.</b></Default>

00:12:19.169 --> 00:12:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it's not like I went out</b></Default>

00:12:20.669 --> 00:12:22.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and got the form
on my own or anything.</b></Default>

00:12:22.919 --> 00:12:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I was thinking, Mai...
-About what?</b></Default>

00:12:25.289 --> 00:12:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to have one
with your name written on it.</b></Default>

00:12:27.919 --> 00:12:30.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would work much better
as a lucky charm that way.</b></Default>

00:12:34.919 --> 00:12:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just my name, though, okay?</b></Default>

00:12:36.830 --> 00:12:37.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scribbling]</b></Default>

00:12:39.039 --> 00:12:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There. Is that okay?</b></Default>

00:12:41.039 --> 00:12:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, my birthday's gonna be
on the 10th next month.</b></Default>

00:12:44.379 --> 00:12:45.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know that.</b></Default>

00:12:45.460 --> 00:12:48.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, that means
on the 10th of next month</b></Default>

00:12:48.750 --> 00:12:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to be 18 years old.</b></Default>

00:12:50.539 --> 00:12:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't submit it
without telling me.</b></Default>

00:12:52.539 --> 00:12:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think being angry
is gonna stop me?</b></Default>

00:12:54.789 --> 00:12:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'll break up with you then.
-What?</b></Default>

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:59.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't it be better
if we submit this together?</b></Default>

00:12:59.629 --> 00:13:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right. Maybe you should
hang on to it for me.</b></Default>

00:13:02.169 --> 00:13:03.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I'm keeping it</b></Default>

00:13:03.750 --> 00:13:05.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how can it be
a good-luck charm for you?</b></Default>

00:13:05.960 --> 00:13:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can see why
it might be confusing at first</b></Default>

00:13:09.039 --> 00:13:11.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you carrying around
a marriage license</b></Default>

00:13:11.460 --> 00:13:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with both our names on it
is better for me.</b></Default>

00:13:14.629 --> 00:13:17.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I guess</b></Default>

00:13:19.710 --> 00:13:20.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah.</b></Default>

00:13:20.710 --> 00:13:24.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I actually have something I was
wanting to show you as well.</b></Default>

00:13:24.330 --> 00:13:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something you want me to see?</b></Default>

00:13:25.919 --> 00:13:28.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Wait.
What are you doing?</b></Default>

00:13:28.879 --> 00:13:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:13:30.580 --> 00:13:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that?</b></Default>

00:13:31.830 --> 00:13:33.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I don't know.</b></Default>

00:13:33.250 --> 00:13:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came home yesterday</b></Default>

00:13:34.669 --> 00:13:37.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>took my school uniform off</b></Default>

00:13:37.129 --> 00:13:39.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks different
from the scar you had before.</b></Default>

00:13:40.460 --> 00:13:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not making
any weird sounds.</b></Default>

00:13:42.580 --> 00:13:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
I noticed it until just now</b></Default>

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I... I don't feel anything
when you touch me there.</b></Default>

00:13:51.919 --> 00:13:53.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even that?</b></Default>

00:13:53.460 --> 00:13:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow. You're putting so much
effort into touching me</b></Default>

00:13:56.539 --> 00:13:57.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I can't feel it.</b></Default>

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you
have to phrase it like that?</b></Default>

00:14:01.580 --> 00:14:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's got you so quiet?</b></Default>

00:14:03.580 --> 00:14:07.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-This is somehow your fault.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:14:07.379 --> 00:14:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're alone in this room.</b></Default>

00:14:10.039 --> 00:14:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

00:14:11.169 --> 00:14:14.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it is my fault
for getting you all worked up.</b></Default>

00:14:14.250 --> 00:14:15.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Kaede is probably going to</b></Default>

00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be getting out of the bath
any minute now.</b></Default>

00:14:18.169 --> 00:14:19.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think so?</b></Default>

00:14:20.629 --> 00:14:21.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.</b></Default>

00:14:22.129 --> 00:14:23.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just a little kiss.</b></Default>

00:14:25.039 --> 00:14:26.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

00:14:41.250 --> 00:14:42.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your phone's ringing.</b></Default>

00:14:42.789 --> 00:14:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have time
for that right now.</b></Default>

00:14:46.629 --> 00:14:48.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Big Brother</b></Default>

00:14:48.629 --> 00:14:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
You take the call, Kaede!</b></Default>

00:14:50.539 --> 00:14:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kaede grumbles, stomps]</b></Default>

00:14:53.919 --> 00:14:56.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens, closes]</b></Default>

00:14:57.379 --> 00:14:59.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps receding]</b></Default>

00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:01.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[picks up receiver]</b></Default>

00:15:04.289 --> 00:15:06.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big Brother, it's Dad!</b></Default>

00:15:07.500 --> 00:15:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both sigh]</b></Default>

00:15:10.580 --> 00:15:12.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna
catch a cold, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:15:12.460 --> 00:15:14.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I wonder
whose fault that would be.</b></Default>

00:15:15.539 --> 00:15:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Dad. What's up?</b></Default>

00:15:17.379 --> 00:15:19.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'm calling about your mother.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:19.379 --> 00:15:20.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah?</b></Default>

00:15:20.500 --> 00:15:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She just got cleared to do{\i0}
{\i1}some recuperation at home.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. So she's getting better.</b></Default>

00:15:25.629 --> 00:15:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:26.539 --> 00:15:29.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I mentioned to her that Kaede{\i0}
{\i1}has been feeling better, too.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:30.379 --> 00:15:31.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She said she wants to see her.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:32.039 --> 00:15:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Mom said that?
{\i1}-Yeah.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:34.379 --> 00:15:36.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on? Is Mom okay?</b></Default>

00:15:36.500 --> 00:15:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Dad, hold on a sec.</b></Default>

00:15:39.289 --> 00:15:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kaede.</b></Default>

00:15:40.580 --> 00:15:42.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, w-what?</b></Default>

00:15:42.379 --> 00:15:43.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want to see Mom?</b></Default>

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:46.830 --> 00:15:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really do.</b></Default>

00:15:48.250 --> 00:15:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to see her.</b></Default>

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:51.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is she?</b></Default>

00:15:51.710 --> 00:15:53.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to go see Mom.</b></Default>

00:15:56.250 --> 00:15:57.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Dad.</b></Default>

00:15:57.250 --> 00:15:58.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[father sobbing]</b></Default>

00:15:59.879 --> 00:16:00.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I heard her.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:16:01.330 --> 00:16:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 7TH</b></Default>

00:16:03.830 --> 00:16:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[bell rings]
-Welcome to Benny's! Oh.</b></Default>

00:16:05.830 --> 00:16:06.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only you.</b></Default>

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm here as a customer today.</b></Default>

00:16:08.919 --> 00:16:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already know.</b></Default>

00:16:10.080 --> 00:16:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't see your name
on the work shift table.</b></Default>

00:16:13.539 --> 00:16:14.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't mean it like that!</b></Default>

00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what?</b></Default>

00:16:15.919 --> 00:16:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't keeping an eye
on when your shifts were.</b></Default>

00:16:18.669 --> 00:16:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was only checking to see
who was on shift today.</b></Default>

00:16:22.039 --> 00:16:24.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't say anything
about that, did I?</b></Default>

00:16:24.289 --> 00:16:26.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure you were having
weird thoughts about it.</b></Default>

00:16:26.919 --> 00:16:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most pubescent boys usually have
weird thoughts about something.</b></Default>

00:16:30.879 --> 00:16:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, you're the worst.</b></Default>

00:16:32.830 --> 00:16:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I was thinking was you look
as cute as you normally do.</b></Default>

00:16:36.169 --> 00:16:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's okay to think</b></Default>

00:16:39.039 --> 00:16:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Cool.
Then I'll stop thinking it.</b></Default>

00:16:41.379 --> 00:16:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I said it was okay
to think that.</b></Default>

00:16:44.169 --> 00:16:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome to Benny's.
Would you like a table for one?</b></Default>

00:16:48.789 --> 00:16:50.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. We'll be a party of two.</b></Default>

00:16:53.419 --> 00:16:56.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Has Kaede decided which schools
she wants to go to?</b></Default>

00:16:56.669 --> 00:16:59.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We went to an orientation
together the other day.</b></Default>

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:01.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She decided
to apply right there.</b></Default>

00:17:02.039 --> 00:17:03.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Great. Glad to hear it.</b></Default>

00:17:04.789 --> 00:17:05.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thing is</b></Default>

00:17:05.960 --> 00:17:07.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to get some advice.</b></Default>

00:17:07.630 --> 00:17:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know everything that's
been going on with our mom?</b></Default>

00:17:10.500 --> 00:17:14.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, she's been in and out
of the hospital a lot recently.</b></Default>

00:17:14.170 --> 00:17:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, she seems to be
doing a lot better lately.</b></Default>

00:17:18.289 --> 00:17:21.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then Mom mentioned
that she wanted to see Kaede.</b></Default>

00:17:21.960 --> 00:17:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:17:23.079 --> 00:17:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked Kaede what she wants</b></Default>

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:28.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she said that
she wants to see Mom.</b></Default>

00:17:28.130 --> 00:17:31.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, of course</b></Default>

00:17:31.250 --> 00:17:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede making that choice
is a really good thing</b></Default>

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter what I think about it.</b></Default>

00:17:35.539 --> 00:17:37.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm having
a hard time deciding</b></Default>

00:17:37.380 --> 00:17:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it's okay for her
to go and see Mom.</b></Default>

00:17:39.750 --> 00:17:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:17:41.039 --> 00:17:43.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're totally acting
like a big brother, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:17:44.329 --> 00:17:45.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big time big brother.</b></Default>

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that supposed to mean?</b></Default>

00:17:48.000 --> 00:17:50.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your natural instinct
is to protect.</b></Default>

00:17:50.289 --> 00:17:53.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that with your guidance</b></Default>

00:17:54.380 --> 00:17:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure that she'll
get through everything okay.</b></Default>

00:17:57.000 --> 00:17:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She probably already realized</b></Default>

00:17:58.630 --> 00:18:01.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that her big brother
is her strongest ally.</b></Default>

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you guys decided on a date?</b></Default>

00:18:05.420 --> 00:18:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to talk to you
about it first</b></Default>

00:18:07.789 --> 00:18:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before we make a decision.</b></Default>

00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think we've gotten
any sort of confirmation</b></Default>

00:18:12.630 --> 00:18:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the hospital
about it yet either</b></Default>

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:16.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm waiting for their reply.</b></Default>

00:18:16.880 --> 00:18:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.
I hope they can see each other.</b></Default>

00:18:20.039 --> 00:18:22.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, are you all right
with everything, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:25.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I remember correctly</b></Default>

00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you haven't seen your mother
in a while either.</b></Default>

00:18:27.710 --> 00:18:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. That's true.
Not in a long time.</b></Default>

00:18:30.579 --> 00:18:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I could ask</b></Default>

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:35.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might be
a little afraid about it.</b></Default>

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just don't know what there is
for us to talk about, you know?</b></Default>

00:18:41.789 --> 00:18:42.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of a person</b></Default>

00:18:42.960 --> 00:18:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you remember
your mother being?</b></Default>

00:18:44.789 --> 00:18:46.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me think.</b></Default>

00:18:46.130 --> 00:18:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's kind of normal, I guess.</b></Default>

00:18:48.670 --> 00:18:50.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I think I kind of remember her{\i0}</b></Default>

00:18:50.420 --> 00:18:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}being really laid-back{\i0}
{\i1}about everything{\i0}.</b></Default>

00:18:53.420 --> 00:18:55.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}But she was a homemaker.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:18:55.420 --> 00:18:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She did everything she could{\i0}
{\i1}to keep the house in shape{\i0}.</b></Default>

00:18:58.539 --> 00:18:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I think...</b></Default>

00:19:02.579 --> 00:19:06.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's surprising how little
we know about our parents.</b></Default>

00:19:06.130 --> 00:19:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. It's weird.</b></Default>

00:19:08.829 --> 00:19:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

00:19:10.829 --> 00:19:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:19:23.500 --> 00:19:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, can we buy strawberries?</b></Default>

00:19:25.630 --> 00:19:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd love to.</b></Default>

00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:30.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go ahead. Pick the one you want.</b></Default>

00:19:30.710 --> 00:19:31.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean it?</b></Default>

00:19:31.710 --> 00:19:33.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, which one should we get?</b></Default>

00:19:37.880 --> 00:19:39.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens, closes]</b></Default>

00:19:39.329 --> 00:19:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm home.</b></Default>

00:19:40.539 --> 00:19:41.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome back, Brother.</b></Default>

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:43.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll make us dinner
in just a minute</b></Default>

00:19:43.880 --> 00:19:45.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-so sit tight.
-Okay.</b></Default>

00:19:46.630 --> 00:19:48.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your graduation is next week.</b></Default>

00:19:49.039 --> 00:19:49.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Yeah.</b></Default>

00:19:50.420 --> 00:19:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have class</b></Default>

00:19:52.710 --> 00:19:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Dad said that he can go.</b></Default>

00:19:54.710 --> 00:19:55.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:19:56.130 --> 00:19:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, one thing.</b></Default>

00:19:57.170 --> 00:19:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai called and wanted to talk
to you a few minutes ago.</b></Default>

00:20:00.039 --> 00:20:01.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was at her shoot
in Yamanashi.</b></Default>

00:20:02.210 --> 00:20:05.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was saying there's something
she wanted to tell you.</b></Default>

00:20:05.210 --> 00:20:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She told me she was gonna
call back. So any minute now.</b></Default>

00:20:08.130 --> 00:20:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

00:20:09.079 --> 00:20:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:20:11.460 --> 00:20:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello? I belong to Mai.</b></Default>

00:20:13.329 --> 00:20:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}Yeah, yeah.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:14.539 --> 00:20:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you still filming
on location?</b></Default>

00:20:16.579 --> 00:20:19.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just got back to the hotel
after we wrapped for the day.</b></Default>

00:20:19.630 --> 00:20:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You must be tired.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:21.329 --> 00:20:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sakuta.
{\i1}-What is it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:23.329 --> 00:20:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got accepted
by the university.</b></Default>

00:20:25.829 --> 00:20:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Congrats. Well done.</b></Default>

00:20:27.710 --> 00:20:28.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Thanks.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:29.329 --> 00:20:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on. I'm surprised
you're not telling me</b></Default>

00:20:31.670 --> 00:20:33.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I need to work harder.</b></Default>

00:20:33.630 --> 00:20:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already know</b></Default>

00:20:35.079 --> 00:20:36.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're working
as hard as you can.</b></Default>

00:20:37.329 --> 00:20:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MARCH 9TH</b></Default>

00:20:40.329 --> 00:20:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And in this case, the fact that
B is smaller than A</b></Default>

00:20:43.829 --> 00:20:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is the condition we need for
this formula to still be true.</b></Default>

00:20:47.329 --> 00:20:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}GRADUATION CEREMONY
THIRD MIDDLE SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:20:50.329 --> 00:20:51.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY]{\i1} Though they were stern</b></Default>

00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:54.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}our teachers guided us{\i0}
{\i1}through these last three years{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:54.630 --> 00:20:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}as gently as they could.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:56.329 --> 00:20:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}We had the support{\i0}
{\i1}of our parents, our families{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:59.539 --> 00:21:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}to keep encouraging us{\i0}
{\i1}through everything.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:02.500 --> 00:21:05.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}We didn't always have{\i0}
{\i1}the chance to be obedient...{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:06.079 --> 00:21:07.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

00:21:09.539 --> 00:21:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[blows nose]</b></Default>

00:21:14.329 --> 00:21:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, how did the graduation go?</b></Default>

00:21:17.289 --> 00:21:19.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, I don't even need to ask.</b></Default>

00:21:19.420 --> 00:21:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a wonderful ceremony.</b></Default>

00:21:22.960 --> 00:21:24.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough about that.</b></Default>

00:21:24.920 --> 00:21:27.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to discuss
your mother's visitation.</b></Default>

00:21:27.960 --> 00:21:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:21:34.039 --> 00:21:35.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Mai.
-Welcome back.</b></Default>

00:21:35.920 --> 00:21:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai said she came to
the graduation ceremony, too.</b></Default>

00:21:39.079 --> 00:21:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I left location first thing
in the morning.</b></Default>

00:21:41.329 --> 00:21:43.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad you could make it.</b></Default>

00:21:43.130 --> 00:21:45.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka said
she'll join us in the evening.</b></Default>

00:21:45.380 --> 00:21:48.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should have
a graduation party for everyone.</b></Default>

00:21:48.170 --> 00:21:49.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you end up seeing Dad?</b></Default>

00:21:49.670 --> 00:21:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but he didn't stay long</b></Default>

00:21:51.210 --> 00:21:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because he was gonna swing by
the hospital to see Mom.</b></Default>

00:21:54.420 --> 00:21:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said she's been feeling
more like herself lately.</b></Default>

00:21:57.750 --> 00:22:00.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to make sure
I asked you first.</b></Default>

00:22:00.170 --> 00:22:03.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know we were talking about
going to see Mom real soon.</b></Default>

00:22:03.710 --> 00:22:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think
about next Sunday?</b></Default>

00:22:07.039 --> 00:22:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you want to do, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:22:13.670 --> 00:22:16.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.
I'll call Dad and tell him</b></Default>

00:22:16.460 --> 00:22:17.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when we're coming by.</b></Default>

00:22:18.380 --> 00:22:21.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 15TH</b></Default>

00:22:22.170 --> 00:22:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think
I look weird in this dress?</b></Default>

00:22:24.500 --> 00:22:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the one
Mai gave you, isn't it?</b></Default>

00:22:26.539 --> 00:22:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Mm-hmm.
-Then there's no way it's weird.</b></Default>

00:22:29.079 --> 00:22:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just because it looks good
when Mai wears it</b></Default>

00:22:31.380 --> 00:22:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doesn't mean it's gonna look
the same on me.</b></Default>

00:22:33.829 --> 00:22:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, let's go.</b></Default>

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:36.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:39.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, look, it started raining.</b></Default>

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:43.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Dad said it was perfect
because he has hay fever.</b></Default>

00:22:43.170 --> 00:22:45.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Oh, yeah? I guess so.</b></Default>

00:22:47.329 --> 00:22:49.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Big Brother?
-Mm?</b></Default>

00:22:49.210 --> 00:22:51.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to buy some pudding
at Yokohama Station.</b></Default>

00:22:51.960 --> 00:22:54.210 line:90% align:center
