<Default><b>{\i1}"March the 15th.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:33:50.079 --> 00:33:53.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Kaede has turned{\i0}
{\i1}into such a brilliant girl.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:33:53.670 --> 00:33:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She's blossoming into a woman.{\i0}
{\i1}I'm so happy.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:33:57.829 --> 00:34:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I want to make sure I can{\i0}
{\i1}be there for Kaede from now on.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:01.210 --> 00:34:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I want all three of us{\i0}
{\i1}to live together."{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:04.539 --> 00:34:05.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"All three."</b></Default>

00:34:05.670 --> 00:34:06.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only three?</b></Default>

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:08.960 line:90% align:center
