00:34:09.579 --> 00:34:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>WANT TO SEE KAEDE</b></Default>

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:12.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>KAEDE WAS...</b></Default>

00:34:12.329 --> 00:34:13.380 line:90% align:center
