00:34:13.460 --> 00:34:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>WITH KAEDE</b></Default>

00:34:16.079 --> 00:34:17.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name isn't in here...</b></Default>

00:34:18.039 --> 00:34:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at all.</b></Default>

00:34:20.079 --> 00:34:21.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no.</b></Default>

00:34:21.750 --> 00:34:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I didn't make eye contact{\i0}
{\i1}with Mom at all yesterday.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:26.579 --> 00:34:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Not even once.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:28.460 --> 00:34:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}To her, it was like{\i0}
{\i1}I didn't show up at all.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:32.079 --> 00:34:33.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that what's going on?</b></Default>

00:34:34.750 --> 00:34:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were together for hours</b></Default>

00:34:38.210 --> 00:34:40.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she didn't say my name once
the whole time.</b></Default>

00:34:41.710 --> 00:34:42.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I...</b></Default>

00:34:43.789 --> 00:34:47.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never gave her the attention
she deserved either.</b></Default>

00:34:48.460 --> 00:34:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}When did it start?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:50.500 --> 00:34:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}When was I cutting myself off{\i0}
{\i1}from Mom without realizing it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:54.829 --> 00:34:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Why was it normal{\i0}
{\i1}for her to not be there?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:34:58.039 --> 00:35:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}When did I get comfortable{\i0}
{\i1}with this without realizing it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:35:03.460 --> 00:35:05.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's why Mom...</b></Default>

00:35:05.130 --> 00:35:06.960 line:90% align:center
