00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[winces]</b></Default>

00:35:12.380 --> 00:35:14.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now I get it.</b></Default>

00:35:14.789 --> 00:35:18.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the spot that linked me
