Are you okay?</b></Default>

00:35:26.829 --> 00:35:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Yeah, I'm fine.</b></Default>

00:35:28.539 --> 00:35:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER]
That's my big, strong girl.</b></Default>

00:35:30.579 --> 00:35:32.460 line:90% align:center
