00:35:39.289 --> 00:35:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure. Got it.</b></Default>

00:35:40.210 --> 00:35:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]{\i1} I was living my life{\i0}</b></Default>

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}doing what I could{\i0}
{\i1}to not think about Mom.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:35:44.960 --> 00:35:46.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is delicious.</b></Default>

00:35:46.789 --> 00:35:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm the one who made it.</b></Default>

00:35:48.460 --> 00:35:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you did an excellent job.</b></Default>

00:35:50.579 --> 00:35:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] It took me a while...</b></Default>

00:35:52.130 --> 00:35:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}I tried{\i0}
{\i1}to forget about Mom.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:35:54.210 --> 00:35:56.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I tried to be happy that way.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:35:57.130 --> 00:35:58.920 line:90% align:center
