00:36:00.539 --> 00:36:02.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Dad, Mom, and Kaede.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:36:03.210 --> 00:36:05.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Just the three of them{\i0}
{\i1}as a family.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:36:13.710 --> 00:36:16.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[waves crashing]
-[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

00:36:33.210 --> 00:36:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wish I could see Mai.</b></Default>

00:36:36.710 --> 00:36:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[GIRL] Mister, are you lost?
-[gasps softly]</b></Default>

00:36:46.539 --> 00:36:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I know where I am.</b></Default>

00:36:48.329 --> 00:36:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think
