00:36:53.670 --> 00:36:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be wandering alone.</b></Default>

00:36:55.039 --> 00:36:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah? Well</b></Default>

00:36:57.579 --> 00:36:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you can really see me, huh?</b></Default>

00:36:59.539 --> 00:37:01.670 line:90% align:center
