00:37:01.750 --> 00:37:03.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I think I might be.</b></Default>

00:37:03.789 --> 00:37:05.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew that you were lost.</b></Default>

00:37:05.960 --> 00:37:07.880 line:90% align:center
