00:37:14.380 --> 00:37:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go.</b></Default>

00:37:16.210 --> 00:37:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:37:33.750 --> 00:37:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}I'm so tired.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:37:39.579 --> 00:37:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'll try to go see her{\i0}
{\i1}tomorrow.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:37:47.420 --> 00:37:48.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I need to see Mai.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:37:53.789 --> 00:37:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Big Brother. [echoing]</b></Default>

00:37:56.789 --> 00:37:58.210 line:90% align:center
