00:38:08.829 --> 00:38:10.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? Is something wrong?</b></Default>

00:38:11.539 --> 00:38:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You... You're here.</b></Default>

00:38:13.380 --> 00:38:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sure am.</b></Default>

00:38:14.579 --> 00:38:16.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you can see me?</b></Default>

00:38:16.500 --> 00:38:18.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is going on with you?</b></Default>

00:38:19.039 --> 00:38:21.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] Kaede</b></Default>

00:38:21.789 --> 00:38:24.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His eyes are open</b></Default>

00:38:29.079 --> 00:38:31.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. This is my room.</b></Default>

00:38:32.789 --> 00:38:35.289 line:90% align:center
