Something weird is going on.</b></Default>

00:38:35.380 --> 00:38:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 17TH</b></Default>

00:38:37.670 --> 00:38:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mom</b></Default>

00:38:40.039 --> 00:38:41.289 line:90% align:center
