00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:47.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here you go.</b></Default>

00:38:47.210 --> 00:38:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:38:48.880 --> 00:38:51.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honey, no work
