00:39:20.329 --> 00:39:22.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Minegahara High School
isn't close at all.</b></Default>

00:39:22.920 --> 00:39:24.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll be going there
in April, Kaede</b></Default>

00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:26.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so make sure
you wake up early too.</b></Default>

00:39:26.920 --> 00:39:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps softly]</b></Default>

00:39:28.329 --> 00:39:30.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, are you sure
