00:40:09.380 --> 00:40:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Oh.</b></Default>

00:40:10.500 --> 00:40:12.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Hey, Kano.</b></Default>

00:40:12.289 --> 00:40:13.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi. Good morning.</b></Default>

00:40:15.170 --> 00:40:17.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just came out here
to throw out the trash.</b></Default>

00:40:18.829 --> 00:40:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kano, while I have you here</b></Default>

00:40:22.329 --> 00:40:23.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:40:23.789 --> 00:40:24.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she...</b></Default>

00:40:25.500 --> 00:40:26.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>getting bullied?</b></Default>

00:40:26.789 --> 00:40:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, gosh. Of course not.</b></Default>

00:40:28.170 --> 00:40:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There hasn't been
anything like that</b></Default>

00:40:30.079 --> 00:40:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not even up to graduation.</b></Default>

00:40:31.670 --> 00:40:32.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

00:40:32.789 --> 00:40:35.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all thanks to
what you did for her</b></Default>

00:40:35.380 --> 00:40:37.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you took over
the broadcast room.</b></Default>

00:40:37.460 --> 00:40:38.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was so amazing.</b></Default>

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did what now?</b></Default>

00:40:41.329 --> 00:40:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. You mean...</b></Default>

00:40:43.079 --> 00:40:45.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should hear the way
she talks about you.</b></Default>

00:40:45.380 --> 00:40:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She says, "I'm so glad
he's my big brother."</b></Default>

00:40:48.500 --> 00:40:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:40:49.789 --> 00:40:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Okay, then.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:40:51.079 --> 00:40:53.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So I somehow{\i0}
{\i1}resolved the bully problem{\i0}</b></Default>

00:40:53.170 --> 00:40:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}by taking over{\i0}
{\i1}some student broadcast.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:40:55.750 --> 00:40:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}What else?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:40:57.000 --> 00:40:58.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So, in this universe</b></Default>

00:40:58.789 --> 00:41:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}our family never broke up</b></Default>

00:41:00.539 --> 00:41:02.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and we all stayed{\i0}
{\i1}in the same house.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:41:03.250 --> 00:41:05.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Mom didn't struggle{\i0}
{\i1}with mental illness</b></Default>

00:41:05.630 --> 00:41:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}so she didn't{\i0}
{\i1}have to be hospitalized.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:41:17.960 --> 00:41:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Sakuta!</b></Default>

00:41:20.750 --> 00:41:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

00:41:21.880 --> 00:41:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}What relationship{\i0}
{\i1}do I have with Toyohama?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:41:24.500 --> 00:41:25.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you being shy?</b></Default>

00:41:25.920 --> 00:41:27.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought
you were gonna take my money.</b></Default>

00:41:27.960 --> 00:41:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would never do that!</b></Default>

00:41:29.329 --> 00:41:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why aren't you in school?</b></Default>

00:41:30.880 --> 00:41:33.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because we're taking
our package photo today.</b></Default>

00:41:33.329 --> 00:41:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Crap, it's almost time
to catch the train!</b></Default>

00:41:35.539 --> 00:41:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ciao!</b></Default>

00:41:36.460 --> 00:41:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wait a second.
Are Mai and I...</b></Default>

00:41:39.670 --> 00:41:41.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[to himself]
Are we in a relationship?</b></Default>

00:41:50.880 --> 00:41:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:41:52.329 --> 00:41:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Morning.</b></Default>

00:41:56.460 --> 00:41:57.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that all I get?</b></Default>

00:41:58.289 --> 00:42:00.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What exactly would you prefer?</b></Default>

00:42:00.210 --> 00:42:02.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want me to say
that you look cute?</b></Default>

00:42:02.250 --> 00:42:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. You know
I did not mean it like that.</b></Default>

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:07.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not okay for a guy
with a girlfriend</b></Default>

00:42:07.130 --> 00:42:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to go around telling other girls
they look cute.</b></Default>

00:42:09.750 --> 00:42:11.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. Girlfriend, huh?</b></Default>

00:42:11.960 --> 00:42:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, Sakurajima</b></Default>

00:42:14.420 --> 00:42:15.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sheesh!</b></Default>

00:42:15.500 --> 00:42:16.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[relieved sigh]</b></Default>

00:42:16.539 --> 00:42:17.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, there's Nana.</b></Default>

00:42:17.670 --> 00:42:20.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll see you later
this afternoon.</b></Default>

00:42:20.170 --> 00:42:21.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You will?
-Really?</b></Default>

00:42:21.750 --> 00:42:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You forgot
about your shift at 4:00?</b></Default>

00:42:23.710 --> 00:42:26.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, I don't know
what's going on today</b></Default>

00:42:26.210 --> 00:42:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you're acting weird.</b></Default>

00:42:28.630 --> 00:42:29.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nana!</b></Default>

00:42:30.130 --> 00:42:30.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

00:42:32.500 --> 00:42:33.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:42:38.670 --> 00:42:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:42:40.880 --> 00:42:42.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning.</b></Default>

00:42:42.460 --> 00:42:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Howdy.</b></Default>

00:42:43.579 --> 00:42:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Morning practice again?</b></Default>

00:42:44.960 --> 00:42:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.
Are you working later today?</b></Default>

00:42:47.250 --> 00:42:49.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am. Heard I start at 4:00.</b></Default>

00:42:49.420 --> 00:42:51.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You needed someone
to tell you that?</b></Default>

00:42:51.380 --> 00:42:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:42:52.630 --> 00:42:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, yeah?</b></Default>

00:42:53.920 --> 00:42:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Your turn today.</b></Default>

00:42:56.079 --> 00:42:57.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Thank you.</b></Default>

00:42:57.920 --> 00:42:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The bell's gonna ring soon.</b></Default>

00:43:03.500 --> 00:43:06.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hey, Kunimi</b></Default>

00:43:06.170 --> 00:43:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUUMA] Huh?
She's in your class.</b></Default>

00:43:08.329 --> 00:43:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ikumi Akagi, I think.</b></Default>

00:43:10.380 --> 00:43:11.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, she is?</b></Default>

00:43:11.420 --> 00:43:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on.
What are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:43:13.329 --> 00:43:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you went
to middle school with her.</b></Default>

00:43:15.630 --> 00:43:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah, I did.</b></Default>

00:43:17.579 --> 00:43:19.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you really sure
you're okay, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:43:21.039 --> 00:43:22.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Akagi.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:43:22.250 --> 00:43:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I can remember hearing{\i0}
{\i1}that name during middle school.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:43:28.329 --> 00:43:30.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}The classmates I have here{\i0}
{\i1}are the same</b></Default>

00:43:31.630 --> 00:43:33.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}except for Ikumi Akagi.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:43:37.500 --> 00:43:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say I understand much
about that girl</b></Default>

00:43:40.079 --> 00:43:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who looks
a lot like Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:43:42.420 --> 00:43:46.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if everything you've told me
in this conversation is true</b></Default>

00:43:46.880 --> 00:43:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>prior to this moment</b></Default>

00:43:50.130 --> 00:43:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then something
subsequently triggered there</b></Default>

00:43:52.579 --> 00:43:55.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to bring you over
into alternate Universe B.</b></Default>

00:43:55.250 --> 00:43:57.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've read some interpretations
of quantum mechanics</b></Default>

00:43:57.920 --> 00:44:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that are supported
by what you've stated here.</b></Default>

00:44:00.329 --> 00:44:02.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Past, present and future
are always available.</b></Default>

00:44:02.710 --> 00:44:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you're saying
they're parallel universes</b></Default>

00:44:05.289 --> 00:44:07.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they can all
exist simultaneously?</b></Default>

00:44:07.420 --> 00:44:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be more accurate to say
that such is true for you</b></Default>

00:44:10.710 --> 00:44:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but as I'm not currently able
to perceive them</b></Default>

00:44:13.170 --> 00:44:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>these parallel universes
do not exist for me.</b></Default>

00:44:15.789 --> 00:44:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. Right.</b></Default>

00:44:18.130 --> 00:44:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How do you think I can
get back to my old universe?</b></Default>

00:44:21.039 --> 00:44:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to say
that all depends on you.</b></Default>

00:44:23.460 --> 00:44:26.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assume you know
what brought you here.</b></Default>

00:44:26.630 --> 00:44:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:44:28.539 --> 00:44:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:44:29.670 --> 00:44:30.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:44:32.130 --> 00:44:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what do you think
about your mom, Futaba?</b></Default>

00:44:35.420 --> 00:44:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you tell me?</b></Default>

00:44:37.880 --> 00:44:38.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, uh...</b></Default>

00:44:39.880 --> 00:44:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think my mother is...</b></Default>

00:44:42.000 --> 00:44:45.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>someone who refused to step into
the role of being a mother.</b></Default>

00:44:45.579 --> 00:44:46.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:44:46.710 --> 00:44:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you become a parent</b></Default>

00:44:48.130 --> 00:44:50.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your life starts to center
itself around your child.</b></Default>

00:44:50.920 --> 00:44:51.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lot of mothers</b></Default>

00:44:51.880 --> 00:44:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>barely get called
by their names anymore.</b></Default>

00:44:54.250 --> 00:44:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For example, she's always</b></Default>

00:44:56.000 --> 00:44:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Sakuta's mom"
or "Kaede's mom</b></Default>

00:44:58.630 --> 00:45:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yeah.
-Yeah.</b></Default>

00:45:00.960 --> 00:45:03.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother was one
who always shied away</b></Default>

00:45:03.130 --> 00:45:05.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from accepting
the title of "Rio's mom."</b></Default>

00:45:06.539 --> 00:45:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She didn't want to focus
everything on raising me.</b></Default>

00:45:10.670 --> 00:45:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was strong.</b></Default>

00:45:12.039 --> 00:45:14.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she didn't want
to use child rearing</b></Default>

00:45:14.460 --> 00:45:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as an excuse
to give up on her dreams...</b></Default>

00:45:16.789 --> 00:45:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:45:18.079 --> 00:45:20.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>...however flawed
her approach might have been.</b></Default>

00:45:20.880 --> 00:45:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're so practical.</b></Default>

00:45:23.000 --> 00:45:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and Kunimi made it easier</b></Default>

00:45:24.750 --> 00:45:26.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for me to start
thinking that way.</b></Default>

00:45:26.789 --> 00:45:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That aside</b></Default>

00:45:27.789 --> 00:45:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when are you going to hurry up
and decide what you want?</b></Default>

00:45:31.079 --> 00:45:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what?</b></Default>

00:45:32.420 --> 00:45:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Going back
to that other universe</b></Default>

00:45:34.250 --> 00:45:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and giving everything
your best shot?</b></Default>

00:45:36.210 --> 00:45:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that really like me, though?</b></Default>

00:45:38.039 --> 00:45:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] Or you could give up</b></Default>

00:45:41.210 --> 00:45:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Well</b></Default>

00:45:43.539 --> 00:45:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] If I were
to hazard a guess</b></Default>

00:45:45.329 --> 00:45:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's something you like more
about this place.</b></Default>

00:45:48.329 --> 00:45:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It allows you to escape
something in your world.</b></Default>

00:45:50.829 --> 00:45:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were supposed to
be nicer to depressed people.</b></Default>

00:45:56.750 --> 00:45:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone vibrating]</b></Default>

00:45:58.250 --> 00:45:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba, your phone's ringing.</b></Default>

00:46:00.000 --> 00:46:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's not me. It's you, right?
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:46:02.960 --> 00:46:04.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone continues vibrating]</b></Default>

00:46:06.750 --> 00:46:07.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

00:46:09.079 --> 00:46:11.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi. I belong to Mai.</b></Default>

00:46:11.130 --> 00:46:12.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}You were slow to answer.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:12.750 --> 00:46:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you that desperate
to hear my voice?</b></Default>

00:46:15.789 --> 00:46:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Sure was.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:16.920 --> 00:46:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Sakuta, what are you{\i0}
{\i1}up to right now?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:21.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was eating my lunch
in the physics prep room.</b></Default>

00:46:21.630 --> 00:46:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Is that a normal place{\i0}
{\i1}to eat food?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:23.500 --> 00:46:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They serve coffee
after your meal</b></Default>

00:46:25.329 --> 00:46:26.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I recommend it.</b></Default>

00:46:26.460 --> 00:46:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You said{\i0}
{\i1}you had work today, right?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:28.500 --> 00:46:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I do.
{\i1}-From what time?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:30.579 --> 00:46:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Four o'clock.</b></Default>

00:46:31.670 --> 00:46:33.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Wanna hang out at my place{\i0}
{\i1}until then?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:33.670 --> 00:46:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only if the two of us
can be all lovey-dovey.</b></Default>

00:46:36.079 --> 00:46:38.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I could help you{\i0}
{\i1}prepare for next year.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:38.789 --> 00:46:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I'd be more interested</b></Default>

00:46:40.329 --> 00:46:42.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you tutored me
in your bunny girl outfit.</b></Default>

00:46:42.630 --> 00:46:45.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}-I threw that out a while ago.{\i0}
-What? No way!</b></Default>

00:46:45.289 --> 00:46:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So, are you coming over or not?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:47.920 --> 00:46:50.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, there was more I wanted
to talk about with Futaba</b></Default>

00:46:50.710 --> 00:46:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll pass for today.</b></Default>

00:46:52.710 --> 00:46:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry, Mai.</b></Default>

00:46:53.829 --> 00:46:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You have nothing{\i0}
{\i1}to apologize for.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:56.420 --> 00:46:57.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, thank you.</b></Default>

00:46:57.789 --> 00:46:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I don't need to be{\i0}
{\i1}thanked for it either.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:46:59.960 --> 00:47:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, I love you.</b></Default>

00:47:01.579 --> 00:47:02.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I know that.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:47:02.789 --> 00:47:03.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I love you a lot.</b></Default>

00:47:04.039 --> 00:47:05.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'm gonna hang up now.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:47:06.710 --> 00:47:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless of the universe</b></Default>

00:47:09.829 --> 00:47:12.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't lying when I told her
that I loved her.</b></Default>

00:47:12.670 --> 00:47:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I'm talking about.</b></Default>

00:47:14.500 --> 00:47:17.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should honestly just use
this time to go on a date.</b></Default>

00:47:17.420 --> 00:47:19.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I see her</b></Default>

00:47:19.750 --> 00:47:20.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With what?</b></Default>

00:47:21.039 --> 00:47:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I see Mai now</b></Default>

00:47:22.420 --> 00:47:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd probably start thinking
to myself that staying here</b></Default>

00:47:25.329 --> 00:47:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and being happy
isn't such a bad idea.</b></Default>

00:47:29.210 --> 00:47:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, tomorrow, be nice
to the other me.</b></Default>

00:47:32.079 --> 00:47:33.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say that
if you're just gonna</b></Default>

00:47:33.920 --> 00:47:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>come right back here for advice.</b></Default>

00:47:35.750 --> 00:47:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can laugh at me if I do.</b></Default>

00:47:42.579 --> 00:47:43.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[locker door closes]</b></Default>

00:47:43.920 --> 00:47:45.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

00:47:51.789 --> 00:47:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So you're
totally okay with it?</b></Default>

00:47:54.380 --> 00:47:56.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] With what, exactly?</b></Default>

00:47:56.460 --> 00:47:58.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Having a conversation
with me.</b></Default>

00:47:58.880 --> 00:48:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] I knew that the rumors</b></Default>

00:48:00.539 --> 00:48:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the hospitalization
incident weren't true.</b></Default>

00:48:03.460 --> 00:48:06.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Then what made you
decide on this high school?</b></Default>

00:48:07.380 --> 00:48:10.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You would've gotten accepted
into a more prestigious school.</b></Default>

00:48:32.880 --> 00:48:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[line ringing]</b></Default>

00:48:37.460 --> 00:48:38.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] {\i1}What is it, Sakuta?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:39.289 --> 00:48:41.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] It's nothing big</b></Default>

00:48:41.880 --> 00:48:45.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did I tell you I'd be home late
because of work?</b></Default>

00:48:45.170 --> 00:48:47.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] {\i1}Yeah, I heard about it{\i0}
{\i1}last night.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:47.420 --> 00:48:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That's why{\i0}
{\i1}I packed you a lunch today.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:48:49.579 --> 00:48:51.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Oh, right. Of course.</b></Default>

00:48:51.460 --> 00:48:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] {\i1}Are you{\i0}
{\i1}still half asle{\i0}ep?</b></Default>

00:48:53.329 --> 00:48:54.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I might be.</b></Default>

00:48:54.829 --> 00:48:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I ate the entire lunch.</b></Default>

00:48:56.710 --> 00:49:00.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs] {\i1}Oh! The rice was{\i0}
{\i1}a bit soft today, wasn't it?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:00.170 --> 00:49:02.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I think I added{\i0}
{\i1}the wrong amount of water.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:02.420 --> 00:49:04.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was perfect
when it cooled down.</b></Default>

00:49:04.539 --> 00:49:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Really?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:05.460 --> 00:49:07.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the chicken, it was good.</b></Default>

00:49:07.420 --> 00:49:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Wow! A compliment{\i0}
{\i1}for little ol' me{\i0}?</b></Default>

00:49:11.289 --> 00:49:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}-Look at you.{\i0}
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:49:13.170 --> 00:49:14.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:14.289 --> 00:49:15.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For what?</b></Default>

00:49:15.670 --> 00:49:17.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}For becoming{\i0}
{\i1}a wonderful big brother.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:17.960 --> 00:49:18.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am?</b></Default>

00:49:18.960 --> 00:49:21.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You've protected Kaede.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:21.539 --> 00:49:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:49:23.210 --> 00:49:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Keep working hard.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:25.210 --> 00:49:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You know, I just...
{\i1}-What?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:30.289 --> 00:49:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind. Forget about it.</b></Default>

00:49:32.000 --> 00:49:34.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}All right.{\i0}
{\i1}Well, be careful, okay?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:49:34.920 --> 00:49:35.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

00:49:38.420 --> 00:49:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:49:54.460 --> 00:49:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Did you get lost
again, mister?</b></Default>

00:49:57.670 --> 00:50:00.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I'm not lost anymore.</b></Default>

00:50:00.130 --> 00:50:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

00:50:01.210 --> 00:50:03.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I know
where I need to go back to.</b></Default>

00:50:03.920 --> 00:50:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going home?</b></Default>

00:50:05.460 --> 00:50:07.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could stay here, you know.</b></Default>

00:50:07.880 --> 00:50:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's tempting.</b></Default>

00:50:09.380 --> 00:50:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This place
is pretty comfortable.</b></Default>

00:50:12.079 --> 00:50:15.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's a little
too comfortable.</b></Default>

00:50:15.579 --> 00:50:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is comfortable bad?</b></Default>

00:50:17.420 --> 00:50:19.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not saying it's a bad thing</b></Default>

00:50:19.789 --> 00:50:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but everyone around me
made do on their own.</b></Default>

00:50:22.539 --> 00:50:23.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who's everyone?</b></Default>

00:50:23.829 --> 00:50:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, first, there's Mai, Koga</b></Default>

00:50:26.130 --> 00:50:28.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then Futaba, and Toyohama</b></Default>

00:50:28.670 --> 00:50:30.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the two Kaedes</b></Default>

00:50:30.210 --> 00:50:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then Shoko{\i1}-chan{\i0}
and Shoko{\i1}-sa{\i0}n.</b></Default>

00:50:33.079 --> 00:50:35.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They got over things
on their own</b></Default>

00:50:35.500 --> 00:50:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I...</b></Default>

00:50:36.539 --> 00:50:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can get over this thing
I have about Mom.</b></Default>

00:50:40.460 --> 00:50:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With all that being said</b></Default>

00:50:41.960 --> 00:50:43.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm counting on you.</b></Default>

00:50:43.789 --> 00:50:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really want to go back
that bad, huh?</b></Default>

00:50:46.579 --> 00:50:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sure do.</b></Default>

00:50:47.539 --> 00:50:49.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you go back there</b></Default>

00:50:49.500 --> 00:50:51.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone you know
won't remember you.</b></Default>

00:50:52.329 --> 00:50:54.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even then, I still
don't wanna stay here.</b></Default>

00:50:54.539 --> 00:50:55.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what?</b></Default>

00:50:55.829 --> 00:50:56.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what.</b></Default>

00:50:57.039 --> 00:50:58.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really really?</b></Default>

00:50:58.289 --> 00:50:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really really.</b></Default>

00:51:03.170 --> 00:51:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

00:51:04.380 --> 00:51:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll help you get back.</b></Default>

00:51:11.789 --> 00:51:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[alarm beeping]</b></Default>

00:51:26.079 --> 00:51:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}I guess I'm back now.</b></Default>

00:51:27.710 --> 00:51:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 18TH</b></Default>

00:51:35.130 --> 00:51:35.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

00:51:36.039 --> 00:51:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>PLEASE GET A GRIP</b></Default>

00:51:39.539 --> 00:51:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, the me from that world
was here instead?</b></Default>

00:51:44.039 --> 00:51:46.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>AND WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT TOKO KIRISHIMA?</b></Default>

00:51:46.829 --> 00:51:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do I think about Toko?</b></Default>

00:51:48.789 --> 00:51:51.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't really have
any thoughts on her.</b></Default>

00:51:52.789 --> 00:51:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"When you get back</b></Default>

00:51:54.210 --> 00:51:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>put the letter inside
the mailbox at Mai's house."</b></Default>

00:51:57.460 --> 00:51:58.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The letter?</b></Default>

00:52:00.039 --> 00:52:00.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:52:02.960 --> 00:52:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'LL GUARANTEE
MAI-SAN'S HAPPINESS</b></Default>

00:52:04.829 --> 00:52:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is none of your business.</b></Default>

00:52:06.579 --> 00:52:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FROM MAI-SAN'S SAKUTA</b></Default>

00:52:08.000 --> 00:52:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I look at this
objectively, it's annoying.</b></Default>

00:52:11.460 --> 00:52:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the handwriting sucks.</b></Default>

00:52:16.500 --> 00:52:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rips page]</b></Default>

00:52:23.210 --> 00:52:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'LL GUARANTEE
MAI-SAN'S HAPPINESS.</b></Default>

00:52:25.079 --> 00:52:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FROM MAI-SAN'S SAKUTA</b></Default>

00:52:27.579 --> 00:52:29.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}If my memory is right</b></Default>

00:52:29.170 --> 00:52:32.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Mai said she was coming back{\i0}
{\i1}from her filming tomorrow.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:32.880 --> 00:52:34.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TO MAI-SAN</b></Default>

00:52:34.789 --> 00:52:35.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Until then</b></Default>

00:52:35.960 --> 00:52:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'll keep spending my time{\i0}
{\i1}like I usually do.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:43.250 --> 00:52:44.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I still have Mai.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:45.750 --> 00:52:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It's fine.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:46.960 --> 00:52:48.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Nothing to worry about.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:48.420 --> 00:52:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:52:51.539 --> 00:52:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It'll be okay.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:53.130 --> 00:52:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Mai will be able to find me{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:55.329 --> 00:52:56.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}once tomorrow comes.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:52:58.210 --> 00:52:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I just have to wait.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:53:13.750 --> 00:53:15.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] I'm closing up
the library.</b></Default>

00:53:16.420 --> 00:53:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody in here, right?</b></Default>

00:53:29.039 --> 00:53:30.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.</b></Default>

00:53:30.170 --> 00:53:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll stick around</b></Default>

00:53:31.500 --> 00:53:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to watch all the lights
get shut off.</b></Default>

00:53:33.829 --> 00:53:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hardly ever get
the chance to see that.</b></Default>

00:54:10.670 --> 00:54:11.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's cold.</b></Default>

00:54:23.380 --> 00:54:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:54:27.039 --> 00:54:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Mai.</b></Default>

00:54:29.170 --> 00:54:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really hope
she gets back here soon.</b></Default>

00:54:37.750 --> 00:54:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:54:40.130 --> 00:54:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

00:54:47.250 --> 00:54:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:54:53.630 --> 00:54:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breath trembling]</b></Default>

00:55:07.500 --> 00:55:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you...</b></Default>

00:55:09.130 --> 00:55:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you wouldn't be back
until tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:55:12.880 --> 00:55:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:55:14.130 --> 00:55:14.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:55:15.829 --> 00:55:18.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Someday, let's have
a family together.</b></Default>

00:55:20.500 --> 00:55:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:55:38.289 --> 00:55:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it really worked.</b></Default>

00:55:39.750 --> 00:55:40.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:55:40.750 --> 00:55:41.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your lucky charm.</b></Default>

00:55:42.000 --> 00:55:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could remember you
because this was with me.</b></Default>

00:55:45.079 --> 00:55:48.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I ended up coming back
a day earlier than I planned.</b></Default>

00:55:48.250 --> 00:55:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw the letter in my mailbox
and thought you would be here.</b></Default>

00:56:02.789 --> 00:56:04.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[whistle blows]
-[doors close]</b></Default>

00:56:07.880 --> 00:56:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

00:56:09.210 --> 00:56:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[yells]</b></Default>

00:56:30.880 --> 00:56:33.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like
a Showa-era breakfast.</b></Default>

00:56:34.579 --> 00:56:35.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the food.</b></Default>

00:56:41.079 --> 00:56:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is good.</b></Default>

00:56:43.210 --> 00:56:46.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After you're done eating</b></Default>

00:56:46.210 --> 00:56:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must be tired.
Make sure you're resting.</b></Default>

00:56:48.500 --> 00:56:50.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should come
in the bath with me</b></Default>

00:56:50.500 --> 00:56:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I can stay there forever.</b></Default>

00:56:52.210 --> 00:56:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I did that</b></Default>

00:56:54.710 --> 00:56:56.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll hop into the bath
after you're done.</b></Default>

00:56:57.380 --> 00:56:59.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I made a stop at the house.</b></Default>

00:56:59.130 --> 00:57:02.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I picked up that sleepover set
you love so much.</b></Default>

00:57:12.170 --> 00:57:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water sloshing]</b></Default>

00:57:14.079 --> 00:57:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What exactly am I wanting to do?</b></Default>

00:57:44.130 --> 00:57:45.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to keep my hands on you</b></Default>

00:57:46.000 --> 00:57:48.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>otherwise you might
run away again.</b></Default>

00:57:50.579 --> 00:57:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just...</b></Default>

00:57:51.750 --> 00:57:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I needed to
forget about my mother</b></Default>

00:57:53.579 --> 00:57:54.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in order to survive.</b></Default>

00:57:55.880 --> 00:57:57.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I moved here with Kaede</b></Default>

00:57:57.380 --> 00:57:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right after
she lost her memory.</b></Default>

00:58:00.789 --> 00:58:04.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that life, I couldn't rely
on Mom or Dad for anything.</b></Default>

00:58:05.710 --> 00:58:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I woke up on my own
in the morning</b></Default>

00:58:08.079 --> 00:58:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I made meals</b></Default>

00:58:09.670 --> 00:58:10.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did the laundry.</b></Default>

00:58:11.460 --> 00:58:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I cleaned the whole house</b></Default>

00:58:14.079 --> 00:58:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I took the trash out.</b></Default>

00:58:16.750 --> 00:58:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to do everything.</b></Default>

00:58:19.170 --> 00:58:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I learned
how to do everything.</b></Default>

00:58:22.250 --> 00:58:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to be strong alone</b></Default>

00:58:24.250 --> 00:58:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without my mother
being around to help me.</b></Default>

00:58:27.710 --> 00:58:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It wasn't like I wanted
to live day after day</b></Default>

00:58:30.079 --> 00:58:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>forgetting about her.</b></Default>

00:58:31.670 --> 00:58:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:58:33.130 --> 00:58:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I didn't have any idea</b></Default>

00:58:34.500 --> 00:58:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when my mom would be
getting better either.</b></Default>

00:58:37.170 --> 00:58:40.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There wasn't a guarantee
she would ever get better.</b></Default>

00:58:40.579 --> 00:58:41.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

00:58:42.079 --> 00:58:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eventually, that just
became the norm.</b></Default>

00:58:45.579 --> 00:58:48.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to force myself
into this lifestyle at first</b></Default>

00:58:49.380 --> 00:58:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the life I'm living now
is really comfortable.</b></Default>

00:58:53.000 --> 00:58:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

00:58:54.710 --> 00:58:56.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is this happening now</b></Default>

00:58:57.170 --> 00:58:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after all this time?</b></Default>

00:58:59.500 --> 00:59:02.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These questions have always
been there under the surface.</b></Default>

00:59:02.500 --> 00:59:05.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It just took me a while
to realize.</b></Default>

00:59:05.380 --> 00:59:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, it's good
that my mom is getting better</b></Default>

00:59:08.670 --> 00:59:10.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's hard for me to accept.</b></Default>

00:59:11.630 --> 00:59:14.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like I'm being
spineless and pathetic.</b></Default>

00:59:16.079 --> 00:59:17.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] There's nothing
wrong with you.</b></Default>

00:59:21.170 --> 00:59:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on. Really?</b></Default>

00:59:23.039 --> 00:59:25.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, you didn't
rely on your parents</b></Default>

00:59:25.960 --> 00:59:28.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and learned to cook</b></Default>

00:59:28.420 --> 00:59:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and take care of you and Kaede
on your own.</b></Default>

00:59:31.079 --> 00:59:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wake yourself up
in the morning</b></Default>

00:59:33.079 --> 00:59:34.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you go to school</b></Default>

00:59:34.920 --> 00:59:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you work to earn your own money.</b></Default>

00:59:37.460 --> 00:59:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a word for people
who do all that.</b></Default>

00:59:39.670 --> 00:59:40.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know what it is?</b></Default>

00:59:42.920 --> 00:59:43.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-mm.</b></Default>

00:59:45.829 --> 00:59:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We call them adults.</b></Default>

00:59:47.789 --> 00:59:50.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It just means
that you're all grown-up.</b></Default>

00:59:52.000 --> 00:59:54.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffling]</b></Default>

01:00:03.250 --> 01:00:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

01:00:14.500 --> 01:00:17.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 19TH</b></Default>

01:00:28.579 --> 01:00:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Morning.</b></Default>

01:00:30.130 --> 01:00:32.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning, pretty lady.</b></Default>

01:00:35.710 --> 01:00:36.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

01:00:36.920 --> 01:00:38.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just wanted to make sure</b></Default>

01:00:38.289 --> 01:00:39.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you didn't take off
my underwear.</b></Default>

01:00:40.079 --> 01:00:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd never do that
without consent.</b></Default>

01:00:41.960 --> 01:00:43.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sure about that?</b></Default>

01:00:44.670 --> 01:00:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only gave you a kiss.</b></Default>

01:00:49.670 --> 01:00:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You did?!</b></Default>

01:00:51.000 --> 01:00:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, Sakuta, enough!
Get away from me.</b></Default>

01:00:53.579 --> 01:00:55.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You're too cute!
I can't...</b></Default>

01:00:55.630 --> 01:00:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both grunting]</b></Default>

01:00:59.079 --> 01:01:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mai chuckles softly]</b></Default>

01:01:00.329 --> 01:01:01.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] This is a special case.</b></Default>

01:01:10.130 --> 01:01:11.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man</b></Default>

01:01:11.630 --> 01:01:13.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this is just what I needed.</b></Default>

01:01:15.500 --> 01:01:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Five more seconds, okay?</b></Default>

01:01:18.539 --> 01:01:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

01:01:20.039 --> 01:01:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want five more hours.</b></Default>

01:01:22.079 --> 01:01:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Five minutes.</b></Default>

01:01:23.789 --> 01:01:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should have said five days.</b></Default>

01:01:25.789 --> 01:01:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be ridiculous.</b></Default>

01:01:29.579 --> 01:01:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, what's your plan today?</b></Default>

01:01:32.329 --> 01:01:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's yours?</b></Default>

01:01:33.829 --> 01:01:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm right back to work.</b></Default>

01:01:35.579 --> 01:01:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm still shooting that film
in Yamanashi.</b></Default>

01:01:38.170 --> 01:01:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

01:01:39.539 --> 01:01:41.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You didn't get any sleep.</b></Default>

01:01:41.670 --> 01:01:44.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was going to have Ryoko
drive me back out there.</b></Default>

01:01:44.670 --> 01:01:46.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can take a nap on the way.</b></Default>

01:01:47.630 --> 01:01:49.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about you, Sakuta?</b></Default>

01:01:50.250 --> 01:01:52.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to pay a visit to Mom.</b></Default>

01:01:52.670 --> 01:01:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're okay alone?</b></Default>

01:01:55.039 --> 01:01:58.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think I know.
It has to happen.</b></Default>

01:01:58.289 --> 01:02:00.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I can get through it.</b></Default>

01:02:01.460 --> 01:02:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine.
I need to see my mom again.</b></Default>

01:02:04.960 --> 01:02:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When things calm down</b></Default>

01:02:06.539 --> 01:02:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really want you to
introduce me to your mother.</b></Default>

01:02:09.880 --> 01:02:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think you can do that for me?</b></Default>

01:02:17.539 --> 01:02:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

01:02:21.579 --> 01:02:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[tap running]
-[dishes clinking]</b></Default>

01:02:28.960 --> 01:02:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

01:02:43.750 --> 01:02:45.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>AZUSAGAWA</b></Default>

01:02:48.500 --> 01:02:49.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[unlocks door]</b></Default>

01:02:55.329 --> 01:02:56.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mom?</b></Default>

01:02:56.630 --> 01:02:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede?</b></Default>

01:02:58.829 --> 01:03:00.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did they end up going somewhere?</b></Default>

01:03:05.630 --> 01:03:07.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}OUTPATIENT VISIT</b></Default>

01:03:35.289 --> 01:03:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which one of these
hospital rooms is Mom's?</b></Default>

01:03:38.539 --> 01:03:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, since I'm invisible</b></Default>

01:03:40.829 --> 01:03:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll just start opening them
one after another.</b></Default>

01:03:46.539 --> 01:03:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go and see
if I can call Dad.</b></Default>

01:03:57.829 --> 01:04:00.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Having a sister
makes life easier.</b></Default>

01:04:22.630 --> 01:04:24.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I was too eager.</b></Default>

01:04:25.579 --> 01:04:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know.</b></Default>

01:04:48.750 --> 01:04:49.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Mom.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:04:50.039 --> 01:04:51.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She's really trying.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:04:52.579 --> 01:04:54.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Stuffed in this tiny room</b></Default>

01:04:54.750 --> 01:04:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}alone for two years.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:00.630 --> 01:05:03.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Mom, you tried so hard.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:05.880 --> 01:05:07.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}But it's not like...{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:07.960 --> 01:05:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I didn't already know{\i0}
{\i1}all of this.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:10.750 --> 01:05:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It was so tough{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:12.039 --> 01:05:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}because she was trying.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:13.829 --> 01:05:15.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffles]</b></Default>

01:05:15.130 --> 01:05:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to thank you, Mom.</b></Default>

01:05:17.539 --> 01:05:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You never gave up.</b></Default>

01:05:19.960 --> 01:05:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for getting better.</b></Default>

01:05:22.130 --> 01:05:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for being a mother.</b></Default>

01:05:25.000 --> 01:05:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You gave birth to me.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:27.710 --> 01:05:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}You raised me.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:30.710 --> 01:05:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:33.079 --> 01:05:34.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'm gonna be all right.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:34.750 --> 01:05:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I promise.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:36.880 --> 01:05:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}No matter{\i0}
{\i1}how many times it takes</b></Default>

01:05:39.460 --> 01:05:41.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'll keep coming back here{\i0}
{\i1}to visit{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:42.210 --> 01:05:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}until you can finally see me.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:05:47.579 --> 01:05:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye, Mom.</b></Default>

01:05:48.710 --> 01:05:49.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be back soon.</b></Default>

01:05:58.170 --> 01:05:59.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MOTHER] Sakuta.</b></Default>

01:06:03.170 --> 01:06:04.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddering sob]</b></Default>

01:06:09.250 --> 01:06:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see me?</b></Default>

01:06:11.789 --> 01:06:14.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You came all this way to visit?</b></Default>

01:06:16.289 --> 01:06:17.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.</b></Default>

01:06:17.420 --> 01:06:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about school?</b></Default>

01:06:19.130 --> 01:06:21.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're basically
on spring break right now.</b></Default>

01:06:21.460 --> 01:06:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't
be skipping school.</b></Default>

01:06:23.460 --> 01:06:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I know it's not the best.</b></Default>

01:06:25.710 --> 01:06:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good to see you.</b></Default>

01:06:27.460 --> 01:06:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

01:06:28.750 --> 01:06:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been so long
since I've seen your face.</b></Default>

01:06:40.000 --> 01:06:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really, Mom?</b></Default>

01:06:43.750 --> 01:06:45.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much, Sakuta.</b></Default>

01:06:46.420 --> 01:06:49.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From now on, I'll come back
to visit whenever you want.</b></Default>

01:06:49.750 --> 01:06:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And thank you for Kaede.</b></Default>

01:06:53.670 --> 01:06:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so glad
that you're her big brother.</b></Default>

01:06:59.039 --> 01:07:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry I left it all on you.</b></Default>

01:07:05.750 --> 01:07:08.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I love you
more than anything, Sakuta.</b></Default>

01:07:10.000 --> 01:07:11.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobbing]</b></Default>

01:07:14.210 --> 01:07:16.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm? Big Brother?</b></Default>

01:07:17.289 --> 01:07:18.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Kaede?</b></Default>

01:07:18.920 --> 01:07:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing here?</b></Default>

01:07:21.130 --> 01:07:22.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to see Mom</b></Default>

01:07:22.630 --> 01:07:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and have a proper conversation
with her.</b></Default>

01:07:26.039 --> 01:07:28.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like you did, Kaede.</b></Default>

01:07:42.539 --> 01:07:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all sobbing]</b></Default>

01:08:00.460 --> 01:08:01.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Out of nowhere</b></Default>

01:08:01.789 --> 01:08:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}all of us started{\i0}
{\i1}bawling our eyes out.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:08:04.880 --> 01:08:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}But by letting that out</b></Default>

01:08:06.789 --> 01:08:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}it felt like that's when{\i0}
{\i1}we were a family again.{\i0}</b></Default>

01:08:20.880 --> 01:08:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

01:12:17.579 --> 01:12:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MARCH 21ST</b></Default>

01:12:20.329 --> 01:12:21.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

01:12:21.289 --> 01:12:22.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[YUUMA] Sakuta.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

01:12:22.500 --> 01:12:25.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got a cute customer
waiting for you at table six.</b></Default>

01:12:25.420 --> 01:12:26.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it Mai?</b></Default>

01:12:26.630 --> 01:12:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll see when you go there.</b></Default>

01:12:35.460 --> 01:12:37.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There you are, Sakuta.</b></Default>

01:12:37.170 --> 01:12:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been a while.</b></Default>

01:12:38.210 --> 01:12:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope I'm not being
a bother or anything.</b></Default>

01:12:40.710 --> 01:12:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. I started a break
a minute ago.</b></Default>

01:12:43.289 --> 01:12:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry. I don't wanna hog
too much of your break.</b></Default>

01:12:46.710 --> 01:12:48.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feel free to keep eating.</b></Default>

01:12:48.130 --> 01:12:49.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sweet. Then I will.</b></Default>

01:12:51.880 --> 01:12:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm!</b></Default>

01:12:52.789 --> 01:12:54.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like
you're in good shape.</b></Default>

01:12:54.670 --> 01:12:56.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well</b></Default>

01:12:56.500 --> 01:12:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since I had my surgery.</b></Default>

01:12:58.130 --> 01:12:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all thanks to Mai.</b></Default>

01:12:59.960 --> 01:13:01.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That movie</b></Default>

01:13:01.210 --> 01:13:03.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that one where she played
a girl with heart disease.</b></Default>

01:13:03.920 --> 01:13:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard a ton
of organ donors registered</b></Default>

01:13:06.380 --> 01:13:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after that movie came out.</b></Default>

01:13:08.329 --> 01:13:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Mai tell you if she could
remember me all on her own?</b></Default>

01:13:11.710 --> 01:13:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. She forgot about you.</b></Default>

01:13:14.500 --> 01:13:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of us
had the same experience.</b></Default>

01:13:16.920 --> 01:13:19.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She remembered on the way home
from the shrine</b></Default>

01:13:19.380 --> 01:13:20.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>back when she saw you again</b></Default>

01:13:20.880 --> 01:13:23.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the shores of Shichirigahama
on New Year's.</b></Default>

01:13:23.960 --> 01:13:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what brings you here?</b></Default>

01:13:26.250 --> 01:13:29.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm moving.
I wanted to tell you in person.</b></Default>

01:13:29.170 --> 01:13:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where to?</b></Default>

01:13:30.329 --> 01:13:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To Okinawa.</b></Default>

01:13:31.670 --> 01:13:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm in a warmer area</b></Default>

01:13:33.039 --> 01:13:35.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it isn't as hard for my body
to keep going.</b></Default>

01:13:35.829 --> 01:13:38.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After I get settled in</b></Default>

01:13:38.539 --> 01:13:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okinawa, huh? Sounds great.</b></Default>

01:13:41.210 --> 01:13:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll send you a letter when I
get used to things over there.</b></Default>

01:13:44.380 --> 01:13:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be waiting.
You'd better send pictures too.</b></Default>

01:13:47.039 --> 01:13:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

01:13:48.079 --> 01:13:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be sure
to enclose a swimsuit shot.</b></Default>

01:13:50.500 --> 01:13:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please wait three years
to do that.</b></Default>

01:13:52.329 --> 01:13:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In three years then.</b></Default>

01:13:53.920 --> 01:13:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll mail you something that'll
make you have a fight with Mai.</b></Default>

01:13:57.250 --> 01:13:58.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking forward to that.</b></Default>

01:13:58.829 --> 01:14:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes! [chuckles]</b></Default>

01:14:00.289 --> 01:14:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah.
There was something else</b></Default>

01:14:02.579 --> 01:14:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I thought
I should bring up today.</b></Default>

01:14:04.960 --> 01:14:05.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

01:14:06.039 --> 01:14:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is something
slightly concerning.</b></Default>

01:14:08.579 --> 01:14:09.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

01:14:09.880 --> 01:14:12.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can still remember everything.</b></Default>

01:14:12.420 --> 01:14:14.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and Mai
don't have those memories</b></Default>

01:14:15.000 --> 01:14:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it seems like
